{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Can You Escape in Time? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/AD_inline_media_02.gif?t=1736475417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Another Door is an escape room experience that plunges you into a series of immersive, unsettling environments, each with its own unique story and chilling challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make it to the exit either alone or with friends \u2013 the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From a trap-filled lair built by a mad scientist, to a haunted doll's room cursed by the spirit of a dead child, and a secret laboratory where hallucinations blur reality, every episode delivers a fresh and thrilling mystery!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>More Than Meets the Eye</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/AD_inline_media_01.gif?t=1736475417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Another Door offers five distinct episodes, each with a new theme, story, and puzzle mechanics. Players can select episodes as if choosing books from a library, ensuring that no two adventures feel the same.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Ultimate Test</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216330/extras/AD_inline_media_03.gif?t=1736475417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether facing the unknown alone or with friends, Another Door delivers an unforgettable VR adventure filled with suspense, teamwork, and intricate puzzles that will push your mind to its limits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0- Find hidden collectibles scattered</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0- Experience five unique themes with their own puzzles</p><p class=\